reviewText: The dubbing is done twice. You start the film and everything is fine with the dubbing, but about 3-4 minutes into the film the dubbing is started again. You have the original dubbing and then you got the same dubbing from the film earlier too. Seven women are nude. Two of them have horrible, butt ugly, disgusting, terrible, cover them darn things up fake breasts. The other five have beautiful real breasts. A couple women are not bald. Usually with a Tinto Brass film you have some still and up close shots. In this film you don't. Everything is very briefly shown or moving so fast. Very disappointed.
